text: Michael Jarboe Sheehan (July 9, 1939 â€“ June 3, 2023) was an American prelate of the Roman Catholic Church.Data Bio He was the eleventh Archbishop of Santa Fe. He was the Bishop of Lubbock from 1983 to 1993. He was born in Wichita, Kansas. In August 2018, Sheehan was diagnosed with Alzheimer's disease. Sheehan died on June 3, 2023, at the age of 83. ==References== Category:1939 births Category:2023 deaths Category:American Roman Catholic bishops Category:People with Alzheimer's disease Category:People from Wichita, Kansas Category:People from Santa Fe, New Mexico
